These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: ebony, azure, black, coral, pink, fuchsia, purple
7 different games are played: go, chess, monopoly, mah-jongg, poker, bridge, whist
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 6. the person who likes azure is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person playing bridge##2
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person who likes black is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes pink##1
12. the person who likes pink is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
14. the person playing bridge is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person playing whist##1
16. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
18. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person playing poker##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Color      | azure  | fuchsia        | pink | black      | coral     | ebony      | purple     |
| Game   | chess | mah-jongg         | whist   | go | bridge    | poker | monopoly |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

